                        <interp inst="t18360613-name-1392" type="given" value="SAMUEL JAMES"></interp>SAMUEL JAMES HALEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I took charge of the prisoner, and have the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Have you ever known me to dishonest in your life? <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> I have known him the last six or seven years residing on the spot—I never knew any thing against him—it is some length of time since I knew him to be in any service—he was then a pot-boy.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I am innocent—I was going for some soap for my mother at the same time.</p>
